{"tid":893150,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"個個都話移民係出路，咁未來香港係咪得返蝻同蝗？","createTime":"2018-11-07T11:51:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-07T17:16:22.000Z","uid":143306,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6c4a67a0b6ccc1b35dff13f9af79feb3d66d1779","tid":893150,"uid":143306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:51:10.000Z","msg":"你班垃圾個撚個都話移民，首先我唔撚理你地實情有能力做到定點，問題係你地心態出現左好大問題。<br />\n移民移民，係咪想放棄香港？<br />\n你班香港人走晒，香港未來由邊個管治？<br />\n總有，你班仆街又鼓吹窮人唔生乜乜乜，係咪想香港未來主人翁唔係由香港人黎擔當？係咪想有隻蝻加入政府？選立法會？做區議員？<br />\n不如落力想下點幫返我地個香港，而唔係淨"},{"pid":"ef4097e38147b24635c755f5e9f25b8d91462006","tid":893150,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70f05ff6b38901510d05390b8d232a25558d1dfe","tid":893150,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a5264ee41b85c77fecbe72847d787ff43eaf7461","tid":893150,"uid":20241,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:54:38.000Z","msg":"你以為你唔走香港就會變呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"382c79f93c21c6c9b97b6ce6e9813fe9ef3492e4","tid":893150,"uid":143306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef4097e38147b24635c755f5e9f25b8d91462006","tid":893150,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:53:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:55:53.000Z","msg":"做返正常就可，唔需要突登唔生"},{"pid":"7927b7c497ff730078967a633e8da05af5a76a8d","tid":893150,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67a9aad8a58b876b8b08960ec60a998803fc050f","tid":893150,"uid":143306,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"70f05ff6b38901510d05390b8d232a25558d1dfe","tid":893150,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-07T11:54:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"re